{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"visibility","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/visibility","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p><code>visibility</code>属性让你能够控制一个图形元素的可见性。用了值<code>hidden</code>或者值<code>collapse</code>，当前的图形元素将不可见。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\"><strong>注意：</strong>如果 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code></a>元素、<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code></a>元素或<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/altGlyph\"><code>&lt;altGlyph&gt;</code></a>元素上的<code>visibility</code>属性设置为<code>hidden</code>，则文本变得不可见，但是依然占用文本布局计算的空间。</div>\n\n<p>根据属性<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/pointer-events\">pointer-events</a></code>的值，图形元素如果属性<code>visibility 值设置为 hidden，依然能够响应事件。</code></p>\n\n<p>作为一个外观属性，它可以直接用作 CSS 样式表内部的属性。请阅读<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/visibility\"><code>css visibility</code></a>以了解更多信息。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>外观属性</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><strong>visible</strong> | hidden | collapse | inherit</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/painting.html#VisibilityProperty\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素楞以使用<code>visibility</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#graphics\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Graphics\">图形元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#text_content_elements\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Text_content_elements\">文本内容元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>属性<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/display\">display</a></code>&nbsp;</li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/visibility\"><code>css visibility</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"visibility","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/visibility","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/visibility/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/visibility","title":"visibility"}],"pageTitle":"visibility - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}